title: Trender Bender 4/9: 799, Robert E Lee, Kaepernick, Sbarro and Auntie Anne's,
itunes:title: Trender Bender 4/9: 799, Robert E Lee, Kaepernick, Sbarro and Auntie Anne's,
description:
On this episode of Trender Bender Jack and Miles discuss how 799 New Yorkers passed today alone, today is Confederate Surrender day, Colin Kaepernick is trending because of a fake announcement he was going to the Jets, and a challenge was thrown to the internet about which mall staple you would pick.
